			description: [
				"§bEnchanted: Witchcraft§r is a witchcraft-themed magic mod covering four core disciplines:"
				""
				"\u2022 §bHerbology§r \u2014 grow a witch\u2019s garden of magical herbs, trees, and plants"
				"\u2022 §bCircle Magic§r \u2014 draw chalk ritual circles to perform 45+ rites on the world"
				"\u2022 §bBrewing§r \u2014 craft potions in the Witch\u2019s Cauldron or Kettle using herbs and ingredients"
				"\u2022 §bPoppetry§r \u2014 craft protective poppets to shield from death, or voodoo poppets to inflict status effects"
				""
				"Start by crafting the §6Art of Witchcraft§r guidebook: combine a §eBook§r, §eInk Sac§r, §eFeather§r, and §eBelladonna Seeds§r in your crafting grid. Belladonna seeds drop from breaking grass."
			]
			icon: "enchanted:broom"
			id: "9A00"
			optional: true
			size: 1.5d
			subtitle: "Click to learn more"
			tasks: [{
