				title: "Enchanted: Witchcraft Overview"
				type: "checkmark"
			}]
			title: "\u2728 Witchcraft"
			x: 0.0d
			y: 0.0d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["9A00"]
			description: [
				"§6Belladonna Seeds§r are the starting ingredient for the §bEnchanted: Witchcraft§r mod. They drop from breaking grass, just like wheat seeds."
				""
				"Collect a few and combine them with a §eBook§r, §eInk Sac§r, and §eFeather§r in your crafting grid to create the §6Art of Witchcraft§r \u2014 the in-game guidebook for the mod."
				""
				"The guidebook explains every recipe, ritual, and mechanic in the mod with illustrated pages. Keep it in your inventory whenever you are experimenting."
				""
				"You can also grow Belladonna plants as part of your §eHerbology§r garden \u2014 they are ingredients in several brewing recipes."
			]
			icon: "enchanted:belladonna_seeds"
			id: "9A02"
			tasks: [{
				id: "9B02"
				item: "enchanted:belladonna_seeds"
				type: "item"
