		{
			dependencies: ["9A02"]
			description: [
				"Craft the §6Art of Witchcraft§r guidebook using §eBelladonna Seeds§r + §eBook§r + §eInk Sac§r + §eFeather§r in any crafting grid arrangement."
				""
				"This book is your primary reference for all §bEnchanted: Witchcraft§r content. It documents every ritual, brewing recipe, poppet type, and herb in the mod."
				""
				"Read through the Herbology chapter first \u2014 growing your own ingredient garden makes all other disciplines much easier to progress through."
			]
