		{
			dependencies: ["9A00"]
			description: [
				"§bBrewing§r in §bEnchanted: Witchcraft§r uses the §6Witch\u2019s Cauldron§r and §6Witch\u2019s Kettle§r to create unique potions and concoctions."
				""
				"The Cauldron accepts herbs, mushrooms, and magical ingredients. Add items one at a time and stir with a wooden spoon. The recipe book in the §6Art of Witchcraft§r lists all available brews."
				""
				"Witchcraft brews go beyond vanilla potions \u2014 some grant animal forms, alter weather, or create magical effects not available through the standard Brewing Stand."
				""
				"The §6Witch\u2019s Oven§r is used to prepare dried herbs needed in many cauldron recipes."
			]
			icon: "enchanted:witch_cauldron"
			id: "9A05"
			tasks: [{
