		{
			dependencies: ["9A00"]
			description: [
				"§bCircle Magic§r uses §6Ritual Chalk§r drawn in specific patterns on the ground to perform rites."
				""
				"There are 45+ rituals available: from cursing nearby enemies, to protecting crops from trampling, summoning familiars, calling lightning, and more."
				""
				"To perform a rite:"
				"1. Draw the correct chalk circle pattern on the ground"
				"2. Place the required ingredient items in the center"
				"3. Activate with a right-click"
				""
				"The §6Art of Witchcraft§r guidebook documents all ritual patterns and ingredient requirements. §6Golden Chalk§r creates permanent circles; §6Ritual Chalk§r creates single-use ones."
			]
			icon: "enchanted:ritual_chalk"
			id: "9A06"
			tasks: [{
