		{
			dependencies: ["9A00"]
			description: [
				"§bPoppetry§r lets you craft poppets \u2014 small cloth dolls with magical properties."
				""
				"Two types exist:"
				"\u2022 §6Protective Poppets§r \u2014 placed in your inventory or on a stand, they absorb lethal damage on your behalf and save your life. They are consumed in the process."
				"\u2022 §6Voodoo Poppets§r \u2014 requires a piece of the target\u2019s hair or blood. Used to inflict status effects on a specific entity at range."
				""
				"Protective poppets are earned through the Witchcraft progression. They require specific herbs and magical items to craft \u2014 consult the §6Art of Witchcraft§r for recipes."
			]
