				"The §6Broom§r allows you to fly freely in the overworld \u2014 no fuel, no limits."
				""
				"Craft the §6Broom§r at a crafting table using wood, string, and sticks. Right-click to mount and press Jump to ascend. Sneak to dismount."
				""
				"The §6Enchanted Broomstick§r is an upgraded variant with greater speed and altitude. It is obtained by enchanting a regular broom at the §6Witch\u2019s Altar§r \u2014 a multiblock structure built as part of the witchcraft progression."
				""
